Package org.lfj.lang.util

Class ManualTypeDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfj.lang.util.TypeDispatcher
      • org.lfj.lang.util.ManualTypeDispatcher
  • public class ManualTypeDispatcher
extends TypeDispatcher
    This is a manual type dispatcher which allows you to dispatch types based upon a set of declared specs. This is used to do reflection upon currently being defined classes that haven't yet been loaded into memory by the compiler.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      ManualTypeDispatcher​(MemberSpec[] specs, TypeDispatcher fallbackDispatcher)
      Construct a manual type dispatcher from an array of declared specs and its fallback dispatcher to be used when there is no name matching specs among the declared specs.
